****************************************
**** Displaying Toast Notifications ****
****************************************
Aka - slide panel notifications.

1- install react-toastify: npm i react-toastify

in app.js import import { ToastContainer, toast } from "react-toastify";

2- also  import "react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css";

3- in httpService.js import { toast } from "react-toastify";
	toast is a function, but can also be used like an object and can directly replace the "alert" functions used for errors.
	IE: you can call toast("text") 
	or you can call toast.error("error text")
	there is also toast.success() and toast.info()
	it just changes the presentation of the toast
